/svg"&gt;&lt;path d="M23.14 10.608 2.253.164A1.559 1.559 0 0 0 0 1.557v20.887a1.558 1.558 0 0 0 2.253 1.392L23.14 13.393a1.557 1.557 0 0 0 0-2.785Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button&gt;&lt;svg viewbox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"&gt;&lt;rect height="22" rx="1.5" ry="1.5" width="7" x="3" y="1"&gt;&lt;rect height="22" rx="1.5" ry="1.5" width="7" x="14" y="1"&gt;&lt;/rect&gt;&lt;/rect&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/button&gt;0:00/16.176&lt;input max="100" type="range" value="0"/&gt;&lt;button&gt;1×&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button&gt;&lt;svg viewbox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"&gt;&lt;path d="M15.189 2.021a9.728 9.728 0 0 0-7.924 4.85.249.249 0 0 1-.221.133H5.25a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v2a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h1.794a.249.249 0 0 1 .221.133 9.73 9.73 0 0 0 7.924 4.85h.06a1 1 0 0 0 1-1V3.02a1 1 0 0 0-1.06-.998Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button&gt;&lt;svg viewbox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"&gt;&lt;path d="M16.177 4.3a.248.248 0 0 0 .073-.176v-1.1a1 1 0 0 0-1.061-1 9.728 9.728 0 0 0-7.924 4.85.249.249 0 0 1-.221.133H5.25a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v2a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h.114a.251.251 0 0 0 .177-.073ZM23.707 1.706A1 1 0 0 0 22.293.292l-22 22a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.414l.009.009a1 1 0 0 0 1.405-.009l6.63-6.631A.251.251 0 0 1 8.515 17a.245.245 0 0 1 .177.075 10.081 10.081 0 0 0 6.5 2.92 1 1 0 0 0 1.061-1V9.266a.247.247 0 0 1 .073-.176Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/button&gt;&lt;input max="100" type="range" value="100"/&gt;&lt;p&gt;这三者都将为Copilot、Teams和Azure Speech提供支持，并契合Build大会所面向的开发者群体。这一时机恰逢更大规模的战略推进——在四月份重新谈判后，穆斯塔法·苏莱曼的团队正引导公司逐步脱离OpenAI。有报道指出，届时还将有一款自研的&lt;a href="https://www.theinformation.com/newsletters/ai-agenda/microsoft-release-new-coding-model-next-week-comeback-attempt?utm_campaign=Brand+Partnerships&amp;amp;utm_content=PwC&amp;amp;utm_medium=organic_social&amp;amp;utm_source=bluesky%2Cfacebook%2Cthreads%2Ctwitter&amp;amp;rc=hnvqnq"&gt;编程模型&lt;/a&gt;亮相，用于GitHub Copilot，而一款整合聊天、编程和智能体功能的Copilot“&lt;a href="https://sources.news/p/leaked-microsoft-ai-copilot-super-app-autopilot-scout?ref=testingcatalog.com"&gt;超级应用&lt;/a&gt;”预计将在夏末推出，将各项功能集中于一个统一平台。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 22:36:10 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>